title: # 34 - Open Tabs
description:
Welcome to Open Tabs! The show where I leave all of the tabs open on my browser and go through them with you! 

Today, I go through YBS Youngblood’s first time drinking coffee, Robin Hood’s Arrow, home made ravioli, Jennifer Nettles, Best Ever Food Review Show, DJ Premier, Bob James, Snoop Dogg’s Wine, and my favorite Weezer cover band! 

 

For all TOUR DATE & MERCH click HERE: http://www.bertbertbert.com
